review_blob: 220z bomber generously shared by nuplastikk.  This beer is gross.  Tastes like infected hairspray.  The aftertaste is overly sweet like breadfruit, which is gross. The color is nice.

750ml bottle, smoky aroma, thick, dark brown color and texture.  Very heavy and extremely smooth.  Delicious sour coffee flavor, thick and sweet with just enough carbonation and effervescence to balance the maltiness.
beer_name: Mikkeller X-mas Porter 2008 Fra Til (From To)
